== Art and architecture ==
The dynasty patronized [[Shaivism]] and [[Vaishnavism]], but were tolerant towards [[Buddhism]] and [[Jainism]]. Several temples were constructed during their reign in Kadwaha.<ref name="TSP_ASI_Kadwaha"/>

